'''[[inverse]] [[matrix]]'''

#{{linearalg}} Of a [[matrix]] A, another matrix B such that A multiplied by B and B multiplied by A both equal the [[identity matrix]].<!--Note: matrix multiplication is not commutative, so B x A is not the same as A x B; both of the stated conditions must hold for matrix B to be the inverse matrix of matrix A-->

